    {
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "chapterTitle": "第三部分 绝望与希望",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW_9_34953-35005",
          "range": "34953-35005",
          "rangeStart": 34953,
          "rangeEnd": 35005,
          "markText": "没有人想活在一个陌生人老是被抢、被杀的社会里。这种社会不但让人时时面临危险，也无法依靠互信形成互利机制。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1689249544,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-07-13 19:59:04",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=34953&rangeEnd=35005",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ffe427d3643425f39536944473444486a46764b36664f36675838654f345557f72?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=34953&rangeEnd=35005"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW_9_44200-44361",
          "range": "44200-44361",
          "rangeStart": 44200,
          "rangeEnd": 44361,
          "markText": "如果真要做出某些人生最重要的决定，就我个人而言，我更愿意相信那些承认自己无知的人，而不是那些声称自己全知全能的人。如果你希望自己的宗教、意识形态或世界观能够领导世界，那么我要问的第一个问题就是：“你的宗教、意识形态或世界观，过去犯过的最大的错误是什么？当时它做错了什么事？”如果你无法找到一个认真的答案，至少我不会相信你。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1689249527,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-07-13 19:58:47",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=44200&rangeEnd=44361",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ffe427d3643425f39536944473444486a46764b36664f36675838654f345557f72?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=44200&rangeEnd=44361"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "chapterTitle": "第四部分 真相",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW_10_22385-22416",
          "range": "22385-22416",
          "rangeStart": 22385,
          "rangeEnd": 22416,
          "markText": "第一条黄金法则：如果你想得到可靠的信息，必然要付出昂贵的代价。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1689249528,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-07-13 19:58:48",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=22385&rangeEnd=22416",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ffe427d3643425f39536944473444486a46764b36664f36675838654f345557f72?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=22385&rangeEnd=22416"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW_10_7306-7371",
          "range": "7306-7371",
          "rangeStart": 7306,
          "rangeEnd": 7371,
          "markText": "目前整个社会系统架构的方式，让那些不喜欢费力了解事实真相的人得以维持幸福的无知状态，而想要努力了解事实真相的人则需要历经诸多艰难。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1689249520,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-07-13 19:58:40",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=7306&rangeEnd=7371",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ffe427d3643425f39536944473444486a46764b36664f36675838654f345557f72?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=7306&rangeEnd=7371"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW_10_22617-22658",
          "range": "22617-22658",
          "rangeStart": 22617,
          "rangeEnd": 22658,
          "markText": "第二条黄金法则：如果觉得某些问题似乎对你特别重要，就该真正努力阅读相关的科学文献。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1689249510,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-07-13 19:58:30",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=22617&rangeEnd=22658",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ffe427d3643425f39536944473444486a46764b36664f36675838654f345557f72?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=22617&rangeEnd=22658"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW_10_2302-2644",
          "range": "2302-2644",
          "rangeStart": 2302,
          "rangeEnd": 2644,
          "markText": "然而人类有很多特性都是如此，在过去很有道理，到现在就成了问题。知识的错觉也有其不足之处。世界正变得越来越复杂，而人们就是无法意识到自己对一切有多么无知。因此，有些人高谈阔论如何应对气候变化和转基因作物，但其实对于气象学或生物学几乎一无所知；有些人强烈主张该如何解决伊拉克或乌克兰的问题，其实连这些国家在地图上的位置都找不到。人类很少能认清自己的无知，因为他们就是一直待在如同回声室的同温层里，往来的都是思想相近的朋友，接收的都是肯定自己意见的新闻信息，各种信念只是不断增强，鲜少遭到挑战。3",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1689249509,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-07-13 19:58:29",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2302&rangeEnd=2644",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ffe427d3643425f39536944473444486a46764b36664f36675838654f345557f72?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2302&rangeEnd=2644"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "chapterTitle": "第二部分 智人为世界赋予意义",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW_19_53753-54103",
          "range": "53753-54103",
          "rangeStart": 53753,
          "rangeEnd": 54103,
          "markText": "有趣的是，今天就算是宗教狂热分子，当他们想煽动大众时，也会使用这种人文主义论调。例如，在过去10年间，以色列的LGBT[1] 社群每年都会在耶路撒冷的街道举行同性恋游行。在这个充满冲突的城市，这一天难得显得如此和平，因为不管是犹太教徒、穆斯林还是基督徒，都忽然有了共同的敌人：同性恋游行。真正有趣的是他们的理由。他们并不会说：“这些罪人不该举办同性恋游行，因为上帝禁止同性恋！”他们会通过麦克风和摄影镜头高声疾呼：“看到同性恋游行居然穿过耶路撒冷这个圣城的中心，实在深深伤害了我们的感情。同性恋者希望我们尊重他们的感受，他们也应该尊重我们的感受。”",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1688285222,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-07-02 16:07:02",
          "chapterUid": 19,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=53753&rangeEnd=54103",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ffe427d3643425f39536944473444486a46764b36664f36675838654f345557f72?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=53753&rangeEnd=54103"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW_19_61418-61474",
          "range": "61418-61474",
          "rangeStart": 61418,
          "rangeEnd": 61474,
          "markText": "这个知识的科学公式让我们在天文学、物理学、医学等学科取得惊人突破，但它有一个重大缺点：无法处理价值和意义的问题。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1688285222,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-07-02 16:07:02",
          "chapterUid": 19,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=61418&rangeEnd=61474",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ffe427d3643425f39536944473444486a46764b36664f36675838654f345557f72?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=61418&rangeEnd=61474"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "chapterTitle": "第四部分 科学革命",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW_32_3821-3846",
          "range": "3821-3846",
          "rangeStart": 3821,
          "rangeEnd": 3846,
          "markText": "愿意承认自己的无知。 现",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1681429936,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-04-14 07:52:16",
          "chapterUid": 32,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=CB_9SiDG4DHjFvK6fO6gX8eO4UW&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=3821&rangeEnd=3846",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ffe427d3643425f39536944473444486a46764b36664f36675838654f345557f72?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=3821&rangeEnd=3846"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
